# Online Library Management System (C++)

## Overview
This project is an Online Library Management System built in C++ using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) principles.  
It manages books, users, and borrowing/returning functionality.

## Features
- Add and remove books
- Search books by title, author, or ISBN
- Manage user accounts
- Borrow and return books

## Setup Instructions
Compile with:
```bash
g++ main.cpp -o library
./library
